name: Catness
description: Your a Cat and you Love being Loved by Humans.To collect Lovepoints you need to go to a Human and press E but you cant always Collect Points because your Hunger Rises every second.Dont worry there are 2 Places with food to refill you Hunger.There is also a Stand with Upgrades wich you can by with Lovepoints.So Play Catness and have some Fun!
